rows.label: qst003901_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, did the Chief send you over?
You're gonna help us fix the crane,
are you?

rows.label: qst003901_msg0004
rows.name:
That fat wire there.
Wouldn't break from one blow.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0007
rows.name:
Who benefits from the work
getting delayed?

rows.label: qst003901_msg0008
rows.name:
...Whatever. I'll leave finding
the culprit to you.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0009
rows.name:
In the meantime, I need your help with
materials for stringing the wire back up.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0011
rows.name:
You can find 'em easy enough by
salvaging around Gula.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0102
rows.name:
Five Winding Gears. Salvage them
around Gula.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0202
rows.name:
This'll let me fix the crane.
Cheers.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0204
rows.name:
Eh, I don't care. The faster I can fix this
the better for everyone.
